114
00:06:31,724 --> 00:06:33,126
Well,

115
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:36,429
you know, nothing's set
in stone yet, but

116
00:06:36,462 --> 00:06:39,232
Helen and I
are talkin' about
movin' off to Indianapolis.

117
00:06:43,503 --> 00:06:45,338
