00:10:29,328 --> 00:10:33,232
Perfect weather
for all you racing fans,
and who in this town isn't?

193
00:10:33,265 --> 00:10:36,636
Come out and join us
as we wish a fond bon voyage

194
00:10:36,669 --> 00:10:38,804
to the
Miss Madison
team as they load up

195
00:10:38,838 --> 00:10:43,275
and head off to the sunshine
of Miami for the first race
of the season.

196
00:10:43,309 --> 00:10:47,013
