All right, Jimmy,
I wanna talk to you
for a minute.

202
00:11:02,995 --> 00:11:06,265
Listen, this is just
for an emergency, okay?

203
00:11:06,298 --> 00:11:08,267
Now, there's only
about $200 in this account.

